description:
Curb Your Enthusiasm is an American comedy series starring Seinfeld writer, co-creator, and executive producer Larry David as himself. It is produced and broadcast by HBO.

The series was inspired by a 1999 one-hour fake documentary titled Larry David: Curb Your Enthusiasm, which David and HBO originally envisioned as a one-time project (included on disc 3).

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The original DVD's have been resized with DVDFab to DVD5-images (.iso).

Audio: English, French
Subtitles: Dutch, English, French, Greek, Danish, Norwegian, Portugese, Swedish, Arabic, English for the hearing Impaired

Disc 1: Episodes 1-4
Disc 2: Episodes 5-8
Disc 3: Episodes 9 &amp; 10, the original HBO-special, interview with Larry David

